How to Create an Account in Github :
Go to "https://github.com/".
If an account already exists, sign in.
If no account exists, sign up.
The Plus (+) icon will be visible. Click the Plus (+) icon and select **New repository**.
Enter the folder name and click **Create repository**.
Two options will appear: creating a new file or uploading an existing file.
Select **Create a new file**.
After clicking, enter the file name
(eg: test.txt).
Add content and click **Commit changes**.
Enter a commit message and click **Commit changes**.
